 is then\nwhether long-range correlations in finite nuclei which in turn have no\ncounterpart in infinite matter, represent the remaining missing ingredient in\nthis analysis.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Dec 2015 20:11:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-25"}
