rn and the size distribution of the main-belt asteroids\nindicate that the turbulence increased in amplitude relative to the sound speed\nwith increasing distance from the young Sun.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Dec 2015 06:23:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-03"}
